title: Eventer – Collect & Share Memories

creator: Eventer SA
descriptionHtml:
Eventer will make your event unforgettable.

For a private (wedding, birthday, vacation, evening, bar mitzvah,…) or corporate event (teambuilding, incentive, kick-off, networking, activation,…), Eventer will entertain your guests and leave a wonderful souvenir.

It is very simple, you create your event and you invite your guests. Guests connect to the event by invitation link (email, messaging, page, etc.), by QR code or by geolocation.

During the event, each guest adds their photos/videos from their smartphone or computer. Guests can view, like and comment photos and videos.

To animate your event, thanks to the Live Show or the Live Movie, you can scroll the photos on a big screen from a computer. If you have a tablet, use our photobooth (Eventer Booth).

At the end of the event, you can view and share the Eventer Movie, which brings back the best moments of your event with a musical background.

We keep your souvenirs close to you. Whether it is from your smartphone or your computer, it is easy to find the event or the photo/video that matters to you.

Ready for an unforgettable moment?

You can use Eventer for free and with no limitation on the number of guests and the number of photos. You can access your events forever.

Some customizations or options are chargeable. They will make your event even more special and allow Eventer to continue to grow since Eventer is ad-free and we do not resell your data.

Eventer saves space on your smartphone, the app is lightweight, and photos / videos do not use up your memory.

Eventer has no rights to your content, you can delete it at any time. As a guest, you can remain anonymous.

Here is what you can do with Eventer in detail:
- Create an album
- Connect guests by invitation (Facebook, Instagram, Snapchat, Twitter, Whatsapp, Messenger, email, Skype, sms, etc.), QR code or by geo-location.
- Activation by email, Facebook, Linkedin or anonymous
- Take photos and videos from the app.
- Add photos, gifs, videos, boomerangs and live photos to your gallery
- Add effects (masks, glasses, hats, wigs, ...) and text to your photos
- Create a photobooth from a tablet (Eventer Booth)
- Create gifs and slow motion
- Comment & like the content
- Share content (Facebook, Instagram, Snapchat, Twitter, Whatsapp, Messenger, email, Skype,…)
- See the guests and their profiles
- GPS direction to the event
- Research on photos and events
- Sorting on likes
- Real-time assistance in the app
- Access the event and add photos / videos from a computer (Web Eventer).
- There are still other possibilities but you have to install the app to discover them ;-)


Paid options for private events:
- Live Show: Open the internet on a large screen and liven up your evening by scrolling through photos and videos in real time.
- Full Pack: Photos are saved in their original resolutions and formats. Extended video duration up to 30 minutes.
- Personalized filter: Personalize Eventer's camera and photobooth by adding a text (bride and groom, anniversary, name, ..) to your filter.


The pro license offers the following features:
- Live Show (displays the content in real time on large screens) with management of advertisers
- Real-time moderation (blocks inappropriate or hateful content)
- Video up to 30 minutes
- Service of assistance with the installation
- Adding a custom filter
